sub_title: MBA & BSc - Teamleader Project Management at Sysmex Netherlands / Belgium
summary:
As an experienced project manager, I am committed to driving positive change and improving outcomes within the IVD environment. With strong problem-solving and analytical skills, I have a track record of success in process improvement initiatives, and am experienced in a variety of project management standards.

With a Bachelor of Science degree and a Master of Business Administration, I bring both technical expertise and strategic thinking to every project I lead. I enjoy working collaboratively with cross-functional teams to identify challenges, develop solutions, and deliver results that exceed expectations.

In addition to my professional qualifications, I am known for my friendly and social nature, and my ability to build strong relationships with stakeholders at all levels. I believe that effective communication and collaboration are key to successful project outcomes, and I always strive to create a positive, inclusive work environment where everyone can contribute their best ideas
